Hello !

This is my first map i've ever done.

If you think it's good (probably no one will say that), then say it.

If you think the map is bad, then say it.

It would be great if you could give me some feedback.

I made this map in 4 hours. Maybe 5.

What does this map have:
  • Lot of boxes,
  • A very nice, shiny, crystal in the middle,
  • CHAIRS.

What this map dosen't have:
  • Ambient noises,
  • Quality,
  • Proper bot support,
  • A Skybox.

Im sorry if i made a mistake in this text. English isn't my first language.
